lead_paragraph: The Arizona Diamondbacks tried to boost their lineup, getting former NL All-Star shortstop Jean Segura in a five-player trade with the Milwaukee Brewers on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: D-Backs Send Anderson, Hill to Brewers for SS Segura, Wagner
